data.name: description.Text
data.value: A fragrant, bright, beautiful bouquet perfect for capturing that special moment of romance or friendship. Delicate champagne roses with large pink lilies make this signature bouquet a must-have! A premium silk ribbon and cute wrapping complete this gorgeous bouquet.

data.name: description3.Text
data.value: Bask in the light of our Sunday Sunflower arrangement - a bouquet brimming with purple statice flowers, soi, and papua leaves, with a bright golden sunflower right in between. Send this beautiful flower bouquet to someone, and brighten up their day.
